The name '''Chertyl Ruluwoor''' has been used for two different characters. You may either be looking for:
*The '''[[Chertyl Ruluwoor (Selonian)|Selonian]]''' who was sent to [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn's]] [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] unit as a cultural exchange.
*The '''[[Chertyl Ruluwoor (Human)|Human]]''' [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] involved in an investigation about a series of terrorist attacks aimed at [[Selonian/Legends|Selonian]] dens sometime after the destruction of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]].
